Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:55.21,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Hear me, I say cross the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:02:01.35,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H61B0FA&}Can you feel that nothing turns around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.23,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H4090B9&}Like a gear in sync inside a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:13.27,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H60E4E4&}Who can be sure of how to make it work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.98,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H60E4E4&}Recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.49,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H9BB2E5&}Inner sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.49,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H9BB2E5&}Gotta stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.78,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I will never be deceived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.66,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I'm a girl that sees through lies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.00,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Cuz I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.83,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Know it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:33.34,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Gonna fly so high
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.05,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.51,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAFAA4B&}What awaits, and what can it show me now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.72,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAFAA4B&}Smack it down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.22,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H8DC1CE&}Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.47,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H376D14&}Break away, and then let'em catch me say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.35,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}“Don't let me down”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.81,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HBEBA6D&}Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.15,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HBEBA6D&}When the clockwork moves and starts to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:51.94,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}(you got to find)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.77,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Forever let it blow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.40,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Carry out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.99,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H82F7FD&}Show the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.32,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H82F7FD&}Blast it off right
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:10.77,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月がきれいで　僕らは恋に落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:18.60,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ眩しいだけの夏の夜を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:26.48,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愉快なメロディーで　軽いステップ踏んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:34.57,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}笑いながら　口づけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:42.52,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ月がきれいな夜は思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:50.53,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今はこんなに遠く離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:58.56,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}世界でいちばん君が大事だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:09.20,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕がここにいて　歌っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:10.77,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月色皎潔  我們墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:18.60,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}在被耀眼月光籠罩的夏夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:26.48,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}伴著愉悅的旋律  踩著輕快的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:34.57,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}笑著  深深擁吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:42.52,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月色皎潔的夜晚就會回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:50.53,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便現在天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:58.56,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}世界上最愛的還是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:09.20,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我就在這裡  唱著對你的思念
